    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis provides exceptional feedback, with the suspension geometry remaining true and the subframe having undergone proactive inspection. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system refresh, ensuring the thermal efficiency of the S54 remains within spec. While it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity and drivetrain synchromesh are excellent, offering a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
