      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS. This example delivers an engaging, analog experience via its Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high-G loads. Mechanically, the car is in strong health with recent valve clearances performed and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the performance remains sharp, benefiting from a balanced 50/50 weight distribution and responsive hydraulic steering rack. It is a driver\u2019s car through and through, ready for the canyons or the track.",
